en it's below half.  Made over 2 bubbles last night that way, in roughly 3 hours.  Would have been better if some moron hadnt trained Dorn onto me a couple times. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>--------------------------- <BR>
